#### **Endpoint**

`GET https://khaleejtimes-uat-web.qtstage.io/contentapi/v1/goldforexrate`

---

#### **Description**

This endpoint retrieves the gold forex rates.

**Response**

##### **Success (200)**

A JSON object containing detailed information about gold forex rates including gold rate,silver rate,fuel prices etc.

##### **Example Response**

``` json
{
    "status": true,
    "message": "Gold and Forex Rates Fetched",
    "data": {
        "fuel_prices": {
            "Super 98": "2.61",
            "Special 95": "2.50",
            "E Plus 91": "2.43",
            "Diesel": "2.68"
        },
        "uae_draft_rates": {
            "Indian Rupee (INR)": "22.85",
            "Pakistani Rupee (PKR)": "75.62"
        },
